{"type":null,"faqId":37066,"title":"如何使用蓝牙耳机接听电话、挂断电话、拒接电话、回拨电话？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1、接听电话：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接，当有来电时，手环会震动，并且在屏幕上显示来电人的姓名或者电话号码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当蓝牙耳机在腕带时：按下腕带两侧按键取出耳机，手环可自动接通来电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>当蓝牙耳机不在腕带时：短按侧按键即可接通来电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、挂断电话：短按侧按键</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、拒接电话：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>蓝牙耳机在腕带上拒接电话：长按侧按键拒接来电</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>蓝牙耳机不在腕带上拒接电话：长按侧按键拒接来电</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4、回拨电话：</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121728\" style=\"width:0.3201389in;height:0.50069445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>手环是支持回拨未接来电的，如果有未接来电，手环会有一个未接来电的显示。触摸该显示，会进入回拨和取消界面。如果触摸下面来电姓名，取下手环即实现与未接用户就行通话,。如果触摸上面的反箭头，则取消该未接来电。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":209,"faqType":"连接与配对","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2230","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Connection-Paring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":185,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,接听电话,挂断电话,拒接电话,第三方来电,回拨电话","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}